38786>>>        Else Begin
38787>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
38788>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
38789>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
38790>>>        End
38790>>>>
38790>>>    End_Procedure
